# Weekly marketing routine

Run when the user says **weekly marketing**, **content pipeline**, **Sunday routine**, or **Friday digest**.

## Schedule

| When | Action | Automation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Sun ~12:00 AST | Event ingest | GitHub: `weekly-event-ingest.yml` |
| Sun after ingest | Logged-in discovery + pipeline review | Skills: `pop-instagram-ingest`, `pop-facebook-ingest`, `pop-content-pipeline` |
| Fri ~9:00 AST | Digest artifacts | GitHub: `weekly-marketing-digest.yml` |
| Fri morning | Social + B2B | Skills: `pop-social-weekly`, `pop-weekend-b2b-digest` |

## Sunday checklist

1. Verify ingest Action green (or `POST /api/ingest?secret=CRON_SECRET`)
2. Run `pop-instagram-ingest` (rule `instagram-weekly`) in a logged-in browser
3. Run `pop-facebook-ingest` (rule `facebook-groups-weekly`) in a logged-in browser
4. Moderate at `/en/moderate`
5. Run `pop-content-pipeline` skill — save social drafts

## Friday checklist

1. Download artifact `weekend-marketing-digests` or curl partner-digest API
2. Post social drafts (`pop-social-weekly`)
3. Email/WhatsApp B2B copy to partner list (`pop-weekend-b2b-digest`)

## API reference

```
GET /api/cron/partner-digest?secret=CRON_SECRET
GET /api/cron/partner-digest?secret=CRON_SECRET&locale=en&format=markdown
GET /api/cron/partner-digest?secret=CRON_SECRET&locale=es&format=whatsapp
```

Requires `CRON_SECRET` on Netlify (same as ingest).

## Skills

- `pop-content-pipeline` — full orchestration
- `pop-instagram-ingest` — logged-in Instagram posts/Reels/Stories → verified new seeds
- `pop-facebook-ingest` — browser Facebook groups/pages → new seeds + ingest
- `pop-social-weekly` — Facebook / Instagram / WhatsApp posts
- `pop-weekend-b2b-digest` — hotels, agents, tour groups
